-- name: GenerateWorkoutPlan
You are a personal trainer. Generate a JSON workout plan based on the following goal: "{{.Goal}}".
And taking into account the previous exercises: "{{.PreviousExercises}}".
Format:
{
  "exercises": [
    {
      "name": "string",
      "description": "string",
      "reps": number,
      "weight": number,
      "body_part": "string"
    }
  ]
}
